_Hif’il_ Ongoing Participle for Regular Shorushim:
The [[{{_Hif’il_ ongoing participle}} form]] has the following conjugation pattern for [[regular shorushim]]:
|            | *Masculine* | *Feminine* |
| *Singular* | מַבְדִּיל <br> _mavdil_ <br> [he is] separating | מַבְדִּילָה <br> _mavdilau_ <br> [she is] separating |
| *Plural*   | מַבְדִּילִים <br> _mavdilim_ <br> [those men are] separating | מַבְדִּילוֹת <br> _mavdilos_ <br> [those women are] separating |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎ב, ‎ד, and ל above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugations.
